{"title":"MonoGame官方文档(二)","uid":"acf46439f7beafe8650eed8a03f181c0","slug":"MonoGame官方文档(二)","date":"2020-06-11T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-12-18T13:12:34.659Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/MonoGame官方文档(二).json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://images.pexels.com/photos/1030977/pexels-photo-1030977.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=1&w=500","content":"<h1 id=\"添加内容\"><a href=\"#添加内容\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"添加内容\"></a>添加内容</h1><p>这部分内容会添加内容到我们的游戏中去，有关于项目的创建可以参考<a href=\"https://docs.monogame.net/articles/getting_started/1_creating_a_new_project.html\">创建新项目</a>，我们现在需要一些内容放置到我们的游戏中去，对于本教程我们使用下面这个球：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://docs.monogame.net/images/getting_started/ball.png\" alt=\"球\"></p>\n<p>点击鼠标”右键-&gt;图片另存为”命名为ball.png并保存到任意文件夹。</p>\n<p>现在打开项目文件夹并看向左边(也可能是右边)，找到”解决方案资源管理器”窗口。展开<code>content</code>文件夹然后双击打开<code>Content.mgcb</code>文件。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://docs.monogame.net/images/getting_started/3_open_content.png\" alt=\"打开Content.mgcb\"></p>\n<p>我们现在可以看到MGCB编辑器窗口已经打开，如果没有正确打开，需要用”右键-&gt;打开方式-&gt;MonoGame Pipeline Tool”方式打开。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://docs.monogame.net/images/getting_started/3_pipeline_tool.png\" alt=\"MGCB编辑器\"></p>\n<p>游戏中的内容都是通过这个外部工具来进行管理的。可以通过一下方式为游戏添加内容：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>在工具栏的”Add Existing Item”按钮</li>\n<li>在菜单栏的”Edit &gt; Add &gt; Existing Item…”</li>\n<li>在左侧菜单中”right-click &gt; Add &gt; Existing Item…”按钮</li>\n</ul>\n<p>现在我们使用工具栏中的”Add Existing Item”按钮来添加内容。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://docs.monogame.net/images/getting_started/3_add_content.png\" alt=\"添加内容\"></p>\n<p>现在会出现一个选择文件的提示框。选择刚才下载”ball.png”。选择后系统将会询问添加文件是的策略，可以选择设置为默认，然后点击”确定”即可。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://docs.monogame.net/images/getting_started/3_copy_content.png\"></p>\n<p>现在点击工具栏上的”保存”按钮，然后关闭工具。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://docs.monogame.net/images/getting_started/3_save_content.png\"></p>\n<p>现在我们已经把资源引入进来了，现在我们来加载它们。首先我们先声明一个变量，这让我们可以图片加载到内存中。</p>\n<div class=\"language-cs\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">cs</span><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">public</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">class</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Game1</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> : </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Game</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Texture2D</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">ballTexture</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">GraphicsDeviceManager</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">graphics</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>接下来找到LoadContent函数并初始化ballTexture变量：</p>\n<div class=\"language-cs\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">cs</span><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">protected</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">override</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">void</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">LoadContent</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">()</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">    // Create a new SpriteBatch, which can be used to draw textures.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">spriteBatch</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> new </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">SpriteBatch</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">GraphicsDevice</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">    // TODO: use this.Content to load your game content here</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">ballTexture</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Content</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Load</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Texture2D</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&gt;(</span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">&quot;ball&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>最后找到Draw方法，然后将球绘制到屏幕上：</p>\n<div class=\"language-cs\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">cs</span><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">protected</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">override</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">void</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Draw</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">GameTime</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">gameTime</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">graphics</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">GraphicsDevice</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Clear</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Color</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">CornflowerBlue</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">    // TODO: Add your drawing code here</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">spriteBatch</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Begin</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">();</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">spriteBatch</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Draw</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">ballTexture</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, new </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Vector2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">0</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">0</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">), </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Color</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">White</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">spriteBatch</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">End</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">();</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">base</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Draw</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">gameTime</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>现在启动项目，可以看到下图：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://docs.monogame.net/images/getting_started/3_game.png\"></p>\n","text":"添加内容这部分内容会添加内容到我们的游戏中去，有关于项目的创建可以参考创建新项目，我们现在需要一些内容放置到我们的游戏中去，对于本教程我们使用下面这个球： 点击...","permalink":"/post/MonoGame官方文档(二)","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.4k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"游戏开发","slug":"游戏开发","count":10,"path":"api/tags/游戏开发.json"},{"name":"MonoGame","slug":"MonoGame","count":4,"path":"api/tags/MonoGame.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">添加内容</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"天然卷打工战士","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://pic-blog-1255296193.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/touxiang.jpg","link":"/","description":"未看此花时， <br> 此花与汝同归于寂； <br> 来看此花时， <br> 此花颜色一时明白过来。","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/tianranjuan","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"MonoGame Nez跟随角色与固定UI","uid":"e045146adaed8a16cc8d2f3b3398f352","slug":"MonoGame Nez跟随角色与固定UI","date":"2020-06-17T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-12-18T13:12:34.659Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/MonoGame Nez跟随角色与固定UI.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://images.pexels.com/photos/598917/pexels-photo-598917.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=3&h=750&w=1260","text":"摄像机跟随角色框架提供了FollowCamera摄像机来方便的创建跟随摄像机，只需要传入一个实体即可实现对该实体的跟踪。 csCamera.Entity.Add...","permalink":"/post/MonoGame Nez跟随角色与固定UI","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categori